    "extra_descs": [
      {
        "desc": "   This massive codex was placed here by the Halfling God, Jojen.  A thin,\nspiralling script covers its surface, telling the tale of the Graveyard above.\nThe Graveyard is a place where newbie characters are able to become used to the\ncommands of the mud as well as gather a few pieces of equipment that will help\nthem survive the harsh reality of the world.  The mobiles in the Graveyard are\nof both evil and good virtues, so the player may decide which to kill in the\ncase of alignment- driven roleplaying.  The zone itself is to look realistic\nwithin the fantasy realms and will not include any t-shirts, beastly fidos, nor\na Ring of Newbie Helping.  With luck and work, the Graveyard will be enjoyable\nto play and beneficial to the new player as well without the use of cadets,\ntraining dummies, or janitors.",
        "keywords": [
          "codex",
          "stone",
          "massive"
        ]
      }
    ],
